        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_spider.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 412a0063-cdee-42f9-9301-bedf253de39a).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Your contract, should you choose to accept it, is to eliminate four poor souls unfortunate enough to get involved in a scandal years ago regarding a business that was subject to anarchy and was burned down.\r\rCoincidentally, all four targets are scheduled to be in one particularly secluded area away from prying eyes.\r\rElimination through fire is a must. For on this humid, summer day, an &quot;accidental&quot; fire would be the cherry on top for these targets. \r\rGood luck.",
